title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Übermacht Sentinel GTS Livery
content:
Make a statement in the new Cel Shaded livery for the Übermacht Sentinel GTS (Sports) — now available to purchase from Vehicle Workshops citywide or pre-wrapped at the Luxury Autos showroom window.

TIP: Unlock the Trade Price on this sporty saloon by completing a QuickiePharm delivery.
